        <h2>Using WordPress as the Ecosystem</h2>

        <p>Working with Cataluña Cafe, a cozy and vibrant coffee shop in the heart of Barcelona, was an experience I truly enjoyed. As a web designer, nothing excites me more than connecting with new people, understanding their needs, and helping them achieve their goals through great design. Cataluña Cafe had a clear vision — they wanted a website that reflected the warmth and energy of their space while making it easy for customers to engage with their brand.
